Dr. Zhang Jixian observed a group of patients with pneumonia from unknown causes on December 26th. Her hospital reported the Wuhan Jianghan Disease Prevention and Control Center on December 27th.
Initial genetic tests, on December 27, 2019, in samples taken from the patients indicated the presence of a coronary virus of the SARS type.
