WHO only recommends a surgical mask for screening staff at the entry point.
For professionals who collect respiratory specimens, treat or transport patients with COVID-19 without procedures for generating aerosols, WHO recommends a surgical mask, eye protection or facial protection, surgical apron and gloves.
